Quechua Arpenaz 100 Hiking Shoes (By Decathlon) Price: Rs.2183

The need to be one with nature is but a basal instinct in every man. Whenever you’re plagued with the desire to explore the great outdoors, lace up these rugged hiking shoes, grab your compass and set off. These black and grey hiking shoes have been built to tame the wilderness around you, while taking you from one milestone to the next, all at the peak of comfort. The Quechua Arpenac Hiking Shoes have a cushioned footbed and ankle to provide your feet with the support they need, as they navigate all kinds of terrain.

Creating an innovative range of shoes which also comes with unmatched designs, Quechua is a brand that excels in catering to the sports needs of the passionate sportsman. The Novadry concept offers waterproofing and breathability, and these shoes can be used in temperatures as low as -22 degree celcius while active use.\xa0

Footwear Care

Air out your shoes after every wear and clean with a mild detergent.

Quechua Arpenaz 50 Hiking Shoes (By Decathlon) Price: Rs.1119

A long walk with your loved one can be even more comfortable, thanks to this pair of hiking shoes from Quechua. These beige sports shoes can give your feet a good company when you head out for a walk. The eye-catching panel and stitch details will heighten your fashion quotient. Experience a relaxed walk as these shoes come with cushioned footbed and ankles. These Quechua Arpenaz 50 Hiking Shoes will provide you a balanced grip as they have soles with ridges. Team these shoes with a T-shirt and jeans to make a strong impact on others.

If you are looking for rugged, high-performance sports footwear, Quechua is the brand for you. The amalgamation of timeless designs with chic contemporary style makes their casual shoes stand out. These hiking shoes will last for hours in various terrains thanks to its CS system at the heels and rubber outsole with 4 mm studs for great traction.\xa0

Footwear Care

Wipe these shoes with a damp cloth.
